      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this solid and dependable ride! It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a great price. While it shows some honest wear and tear and could use a little TLC to truly shine, it runs well and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of life left, this is the one for you!",
