      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, driveable option for those looking for a budget-friendly entry into this model. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some clear coat peeling on the roof, and a couple of small dings on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is intact but the upholstery shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some minor staining in the carpets. While the car starts and runs reliably, a prospective buyer should be prepared for some upcoming maintenance, as the tires are nearing the end of their life and there is a minor oil seep. It is an honest car that has been used regularly and is priced to reflect its current state.",
