      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
