    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for precise corner exits. Recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe ensure mechanical longevity. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains stiff and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited B-road carving. An honest, mechanically robust example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
